title: Seahawks-Rams TNF Recap, Russell Wilson's perfect night (Football 10/4)
description:
Will Brinson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough recap the Seahawks victory over the Rams while focusing on the spectacular play of Russell Wilson and the case he's making for MVP, if Jared Goff is a problem for Los Angeles and how the NFC West is shaping up after Thursday's game.
